  N5 --> Z1[Outcome: Fewer unplanned stockouts and expedited shipments, lower COGS through optimized BOM integrity and sourcing decisions, improved OTIF, reduced excess inventory and working capital, faster corrective actions for shortages, and measurable improvements in MAPE/stockout rate/working-capital-days.]
