  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Rapid automated mitigation with minimal human intervention; reduced lead time to resolution.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Medium confidence or cost above auto-...| B2[Process Builder creates a CWB Lifecycle approval task for supply planner with recommended actions and impact analysis.]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Human-in-the-loop review ensures governance on higher-cost or higher-impact decisions.]
  O2 --> End[End]
